MOM is DEAD! | Fran Bow ►►► http://bit.ly/2jmegS1

We were determined to see how this game ends, and we were not disappointed. Detention has got to have one of the most beautiful endings to a horror game we've seen. The fact that this story is told through gameplay makes it all the more powerful!
